[試題] 98上 葉俊榮 英美侵權法 期末考











標題[試題] 98上 葉俊榮 英美侵權法 期末考

作者

askrui

                (鬼火在夜裏迷了路。)
            
            


看板

NTU-Exam



時間

                    2010-01-14 01:24:41
            








課程名稱︰英美侵權行為法乙
課程性質︰法律系法學組必修
課程教師︰葉俊榮
開課學院：法律學院
開課系所︰法律系
考試日期（年月日）︰99.01.05
考試時限（分鐘）：110分鐘
是否需發放獎勵金：是
（如未明確表示，則不予發放）

試題 :


1. In modern regulatory states, the violation of statutory requirements
   may have profound impacts on the assesment of liability. Please sketch
   the relationship between statutory violations and the establishment of
   negligence in the light of the cases that we discussed in the case.
   (30%)







2. In the modern economy, individuals are encourage to make decisions and
   bear consequences. Tort law, however, intervenes and reallocates the
   consequences of individual decisions by assigning liability to responsible
   parties. In this connection, decision-making and imformation flow have
   been identified as critical elements in allocating liability. Please
   further elaborate this point by reference to cases we coverd in the class.
   (30%)


3. Proportionality and all-or-nothing are two extreme positions in negligence
   and causation articulation. Please analyze how torts began to cross the
   boundary and come up with innovative solutions in light of the cases you
   read in the class.(30%)


4. Please identify issues or analysis that impressed you most in the class.
   (10%)





